These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, indian, german
There 4 different types of food: apple, cabbage, lettuce, kiwi
1. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
2. the malaysian is not the person eating apple##6
3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the indian is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the person eating apple is not the indian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | malaysian   | german    | indonesian    | indian |
| Sport      | kiwi | apple | lettuce | cabbage |

