.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
House: palace, futuristic, cape-cod, victorian
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, green, blood-red
1. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
3. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
4. the futuristic house is not the person who likes emerald##6
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes green##1
7. the victorian house is on the right of the palace house##1
8. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | futuristic  | cape-cod    | palace | victorian    |
| Food       | blood-red | emerald | green  | grey |

