.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, domino, snooker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, ambient, gospel
1. the person playing snooker is not the fan country##6
2. the fan jazz is not the person playing domino##6
3. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
4. the fan jazz is the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the fan jazz##1
6. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
7. the fan country is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | snooker       | canasta  | backgammon  | domino |
| Job        | ambient | gospel | jazz | country  |

