.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, russian, indonesian, french
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, chef, fisherman, videographer
1. the indonesian is on the left of the french##1
2. the russian is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
3. the videographer is not the russian##6
4. the videographer is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
5. the fisherman is on the right of the chef##1
6. the french is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | russian | indonesian | french     | american |
| Transport   | chef     | fisherman    | paramedic | videographer    |

