.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, blueberry, pear, cabbage
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester, prince, bolivar
1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
3. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
4. the person eating blueberry is not the bolivar-smoker##6
5. the swisher-smoker is not the person eating papaya##6
6. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the prince-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | papaya        | cabbage | pear | blueberry |
| Transport   | bolivar | swisher | ritmeester     | prince   |

