.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, dog, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bike, roller, helicopter
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the ferret is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
5. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
7. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
8. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
9. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | frog | dog    | snake  | ferret   |
| Nationality   | roller  | helicopter | bike | trike |

