.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo, old-henry, game
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, 7up, mirinda
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking 7up is not the siglo-smoker##6
3. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the siglo-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | game | siglo     | old-henry | swisher |
| Music-Genre   | 7up | lemonade | mirinda      | coffee         |

