.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, february, august
City: london, berlin, hamburg, marseilles
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
6. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
8. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person traveling to marseilles##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | october  | september        | february      | august          |
| Job        | london | berlin | marseilles | hamburg |

