2. the owner of the lizard is not the person traveling to london##6
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
8. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | edinburgh  | venice | london    | rome |
| Transport   | lizard | hedgehog | hamster | fish  |

