There 4 different types of food: lime, lemon, raspberry, cauliflower
1. the person eating lime is not the prince-smoker##6
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is not the person eating cauliflower##6
6. the person eating lemon is not the chaman-smoker##6
7. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
8. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | alhambra | prince        | old-henry  | chaman     |
| Sport   | lime     | cauliflower | lemon | raspberry |

