1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
3. the person traveling to hannover is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person traveling to miami and the person who's birthday is in august##2
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | august | february    | october | april |
| Music-Genre   | liverpool         | rome | miami   | hannover     |

