2. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person driving the subway##6
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
6. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
