4. the person eating carrot is not the dutch##6
5. the french is between the dutch and the american##2
6. the german is on the far left or far right##3
7. the german is on the right of the dutch##1
8. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | american | french | dutch | german |
| Pet     | asparagus  | cranberry      | corn  | carrot       |

