.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, domino, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, surfing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
5. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
6. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | mah-jongg | bridge | snooker      | domino   |
| Transport   | cycling  | parkour   | surfing | cricket |

 